{"word":"G5267 - ὑπόδικος - hypódikos - hoop-od'-ee-kos - Guilty","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">ὑπόδικος</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">hypódikos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">hoop-od'-ee-kos</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Guilty</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"குற்றமுள்ள - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"under judgment, one who has lost his suit"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G5259 - ὑπό - hypó - hoop-o'/5259\">G5259</a> and <a href=\"#/G1349 - δίκη - díkē - dee'-kay/1349\">G1349</a>; <i>under sentence</i>, that is, (by implication) <i>condemned:</i> - guilty.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}